      "summary": "A self-contained proof for every k>=3. It constructs the canonical norm-derived radicand gamma_k=2(alpha_k+P), proves gamma_k(gamma_k-4P)=4u beta_k^2, derives universal signed-contact rows (1,0) and (1,1), establishes square-class rank 2 delta_k, and obtains generic normal closure C2^2 wr S_delta_k. The physical entropy interpretation is asserted only for k=4.",
